c: 6
v: 30
t: "And if you saw when they were made to stand before their Nourisher-Sustainer, (and) He said: “Is not this (Resurrection and Accountability) in Truth?” They said: “Yes, by our Nourisher-Sustainer! \" He (i.e., Allah) said: \"So, you people taste the punishment of what you had been disbelieving.”"